@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Sustainable Farming Hub</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/beautiful-view-green-farm-field-600nw-2470800699.webp');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .best-practices {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .practice-card {
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 30%;
            min-width: 250px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .forum-button {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .forum-button a {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 12px 25px;
                background-color: #28a745;
                color: white;
                border-radius: 5px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 1em;
            }

                .forum-button a:hover {
                    background-color: #218838;
                }

        @@media (max-width: 800px) {
            .practice-card {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }


        {
            width: 100%;
        }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sustainable Farming Hub</h1>
        <div class="intro">
            Explore proven techniques that help improve farm productivity while protecting natural resources and preserving soil and water health.
        </div>

        <div class="best-practices">
            <div class="practice-card">
                <h3>Crop Rotation</h3>
                <p>Rotating different crops in the same field helps balance nutrients in the soil and prevents pest buildup, promoting long-term soil health.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="practice-card">
                <h3>Drip Irrigation</h3>
                <p>This water-efficient method delivers moisture directly to plant roots, reducing evaporation and conserving water in dry climates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="practice-card">
                <h3>Composting</h3>
                <p>Compost improves soil structure and fertility using organic waste like crop residue and animal manure, reducing the need for chemical fertilizers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="practice-card">
                <h3>Cover Cropping</h3>
                <p>Growing cover crops like legumes during off-seasons protects soil from erosion and enhances organic matter in the field.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="practice-card">
                <h3>Integrated Pest Management</h3>
                <p>Using natural predators and crop monitoring reduces chemical pesticide use, maintaining ecological balance and crop health.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="forum-button">
            <a href="/Forum/Index">Join the Discussion Forum</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
